BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Brave Little Tailor
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20270607T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20270607T171500
DTSTAMP:20260718T091704Z
UID:occ-1763@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Play
DESCRIPTION:The Grimms' fairy tale of a boastful tailor\, seven swatted fl
 ies\, and some very gullible giants\, from Pumphouse Players.\n\nA stage a
 daptation of the Brothers Grimm fairy tale. A tailor kills seven flies wit
 h one swat\, stitches himself a belt boasting "Seven at One Blow\," and le
 ts everyone assume he means seven men. On the strength of that misundersta
 nding he takes on giants and a scheming king\, armed with nothing but nerv
 e and quick thinking. From Pumphouse Players\, the Cartersville community 
 theatre\, which last staged the tale in 2019.
GEO:34.1644344;-84.7971239
LAST-MODIFIED:20260718T091601Z
LOCATION:Pumphouse Players\, 114 W Main St
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/brave-little-tailor-tickets-1989767364751
END:VEVENT
